0px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>There is also a template for Slater Labs USA, but this wasn’t completed, so it’s more like a quick mockup. The color of the sky changes based on the time.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2004-06-16"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Slater Labs","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/slaterlabs/","source":"work"}}